
console clients:
- ddd, eee, fff, iii are 4 players
- auto login
- auto register to 'testGame'
- start.sh can be used to create OS shortcut (ubuntu, see below)

used resources :
- color cards from http://vectorpaint.yaks.co.nz/


OS shortcut to start 4 players outside Intellij
- create a launcher file with the below content at /home/lumos/.local/share/applications/clients.desktop
- edit the correct path (dont use env vars !, only absolute paths)

[Desktop Entry]
Version=1.0
Type=Application
Name=javaPokerClientsStarter
Icon=/home/lumos/dev/pkr/client/a.png
Exec=/home/lumos/dev/pkr/client/start.sh
Comment=Java console poker clients
Categories=Development;IDE;
Terminal=true
